  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">With this discretionary grant, Ulupwa will improve upon their Maize Meal Project and train small-scale farmers in maize production. They will use grant funds to maintain and renovate their equipment, as well as facilitate a workshop on quality maize production for processing. After the implementation of this project, Ulupwa will be able to buy maize from local farmers and produce mealie meal and other maize-based products. Profits from these activities will help to sustain the organization as Firelight funding phases out.</narrative>
